# tilawa-ui-ux-guard (Cursor rule)

Quality gate for **presentation-layer** UI changes in Tilawa.

Full skill (canonical source):
[`.agents/skills/tilawa-ui-ux-guard/SKILL.md`](../../.agents/skills/tilawa-ui-ux-guard/SKILL.md).

Companion skills:
- [`tilawa-apply-ux-principles`](../../.agents/skills/tilawa-apply-ux-principles/SKILL.md) — flows, placement, states
- [`tilawa-apply-ui-principles`](../../.agents/skills/tilawa-apply-ui-principles/SKILL.md) — composition, components
- [`flutter-apply-tilawa-theming`](../../.agents/skills/flutter-apply-tilawa-theming/SKILL.md) — tokens and colors

## Always check

1. User goal and primary path (≤3 taps from shell for daily actions)
2. Worship-surface placement — no support/tours/popups on reader, prayer, athkar counting
3. **Home:** preserve approved full stack; no redesign/reorder/stale widgets
   unless user requested (see home-dashboard-patterns.md)
4. One primary CTA per viewport; calm copy (no Premium/Unlock/exclamation marketing)
5. Tokens only — no raw hex or magic spacing in features
6. Empty, loading, and error states for lists and customizable sections
7. `TilawaSectionTitle` + sibling `TilawaIconActionButton` for section edit (no fake trailing)
8. `TilawaCard` sibling pattern when nested actions differ from card tap
9. Touch targets ≥ 48 dp (`tokens.minInteractiveDimension`); RTL + text scale 1.4
10. FAB/lists clear `QuranPlayerWidget.fabBottomOffset` when applicable

## Findings format

Use [review-report-template.md](../../.agents/skills/tilawa-ui-ux-guard/references/review-report-template.md):

- **Critical** — placement violation, unapproved Home redesign/reorder, broken path, data loss, a11y blocker
- **Major** — hierarchy, missing states, brand/token break, obscured FAB
- **Minor** — spacing or tone nit

Run `dart analyze` and targeted `flutter test` — this rule is the judgement layer.
